My friend Amy was born in 1995. She's an Aries whereas her boyfriend is a Scorpio. Amy will be throwing a birthday party at her place tomorrow but alas I can't attend because I got work to do. Sarah is assisting with the party preparations. Nicole is also assisting in making preparations for the party. They're sharing the preparation between them so it isn't too much work. Happy birthday Amy. I'm sure your friends will join me in wishing you a very happy birthday. Last year she got me a king size bed for my birthday. I remember I said "I can't believe you got me a king size bed" It didn't come cheap. Nicole has got a commission for an article on Picasso from an art magazine. She's doing research in preparation for the article. Her boyfriend is assisting in the preparation of the research. Her favourite fighter Dan will be fighting John in August for the heavyweight title. Championships like this need adequate preparation. The poster and promo video are in preparation. Dan is doing thorough preparation for this fight as he didn't perform well in his last match because he did very little preparation. John didn't seem to have done much preparation for his last fight too. He almost lost the fight so this time he's doing meticulous preparation for the match including grappling, greco-roman wrestling and kickboxing as well as cardio training. Sparring regularly is good preparation for a match like this. You cannot fight a high level fighter in a championship without proper preparation. My friend Ken is making preparations for his ski trip to Osaka. He's also making preparations to meet his favourite band X Japan in Hiroshima. So he's preoccupied with these preparations. Preparations are being made for next week's ski festival. The organisations and the institutions who organise this ski festival have announced that preparations for this ski festival are under way. Channel one gives detailed coverage of kickboxing fights. John's fight against Dan received widespread media coverage. His fight against Anthony also got wide press coverage. He tends to get lots of newspaper, magazine and television coverage because his fights are exciting to watch. The kickboxing organisation will be holding a chairmanship election tomorrow. Channel one will give the election live coverage. If you wanna check out the reports of John's previous fights their monthly magazines have extensive coverage of them. The book "martial arts techniques" provides good coverage of greco-roman wrestling techniques. Japan Mobile now has nationwide coverage with its network which easily outshines other service providers. Its network coverage used to be poor in Kyoto which affected how people could access the internet but now it's regarded as one of the best. Its coverage is fantastic throughout the country. Ken is a bassoonist. He's looking at a couple of insurance plans and choosing one which provides the most adequate life, health and medical coverage. He's thinking of paying an extra premium to have insurance coverage for accidental damage to his bassoon as well as increasing the insurance cover up to one million yen. Last month, my friend Sarah married Joe, her boyfriend from university. A pastor married them in Rosewood Hotel. I said "Wishing you a lifetime of love and happiness" My elder brother wrote "best wishes on this wonderful journey as you build your new lives together" My younger brother wrote "Thank you for letting us share in this joyful day!
